---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Richard Xiong">
    <main class="about">
        <h1>About</h1>

        <p class="hook">
            Hello, and welcome to my page! My name is Richard Xiong.
            I am a Junior at Virginia Tech pursuing a BS in FinTech and 
            Big Data Analytics as well as minors in Computer Science 
            and Mathematics.  
        </p>

        <p>
            I'm currently an undergraduate researcher studying the effects
            of SAFEs (Simple Agreement for Future Equity) on start up 
            companies. I'm currently applying a fine-tuned GPT model to 
            score SAFE clauses across multiple sentiment categories such 
            as risk, business overview, and financial health.
        </p>

        <p>
            Outside of school, I enjoy cooking and tasting good food, 
            especially with others. I like
            to stay active, whether that's going to the gym or playing 
            table tennis. I am also a F1 fan and hope to see the Shanghai 
            Grand Prix one day.
        </p>
        
        <div class="facts">
            <h2>Fun Facts</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>I can speak Mandarin and Shanghainese</li>
                <li>Brother in Phi Gamma Nu — Professional Entrepreneurship Fraternity</li>
                <li>I have been a tutor since elementary school and through till college</li>
                <li><a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">My resume, if you want the formal version</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 120px 40px 80px;
    }
    h1 { 
        font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px); 
        margin-bottom :36px;
    }
    .hook {
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .about p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .facts {
        margin-top: 48px;
        padding-top: 32px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .facts h2 {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .facts ul {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
    }
    .facts li {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--muted);
    }
    .facts a {
        color: var(--primary);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .facts a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
        border-color: var(--accent);
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .about { padding: 100px 24px 60px;  }
        .hook { font-size: 18px; }
    }
</style>